### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE quantum_experiment_results (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
    experiment_date DATE,
    measurement_1 FLOAT,
    measurement_2 FLOAT
);


CREATE TABLE quantum_experiment_details (
    detail_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    temperature FLOAT,
    pressure FLOAT,
    time_taken INT
);


CREATE TABLE quantum_analysis_results (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    analysis_result TEXT
);

### STATEMENT

DELETE FROM quantum_experiment_details WHERE temperature > 100 AND pressure < 50
